### 1. Health Check
GET https://api.openai.com/v1/models
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Chat Completion (기본 텍스트 생성)
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4.1-mini",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant." },
    { "role": "user", "content": "Tell me a short story about a robot." }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 150
}

###

### 3. Chat Completion — JSON 응답 강제 테스트
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4.1",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Give me weather info for Seoul." }
  ],
  "response_format": {
    "type": "json_schema",
    "json_schema": {
      "name": "weatherSchema",
      "schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "temperature": { "type": "number" },
          "condition": { "type": "string" },
          "humidity": { "type": "number" }
        },
        "required": ["temperature", "condition"]
      }
    }
  }
}

###

### 4. Chat Completion — 스트리밍 테스트
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Accept: text/event-stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4.1-mini",
  "stream": true,
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Write a poem about the ocean." }
  ]
}

###

### 5. Embeddings 생성
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/embeddings
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "text-embedding-3-large",
  "input": "OpenAI provides powerful embedding models."
}

###

### 6. Embeddings — 여러 텍스트 입력
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/embeddings
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "text-embedding-3-small",
  "input": [
    "Hello world!",
    "Machine learning is amazing.",
    "Embeddings help semantic search."
  ]
}

###

### 7. Embeddings — Base64 인코딩
POST https://api.openai.com/v1/embeddings
Authorization: Bearer {{OPENAI_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "text-embedding-3-large",
  "input": "Encoding output as base64",
  "encoding_format": "base64"
}

